{"id":10691,"date":"2023-07-07T14:36:05","date_gmt":"2023-07-07T14:36:05","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/?page_id=10691"},"modified":"2024-01-02T18:04:56","modified_gmt":"2024-01-02T18:04:56","slug":"electionsecurity","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/electionsecurity\/","title":{"rendered":"Election Security"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_section full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1686252359115{background-color: #ffffff !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}&#8221;][vc_row][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_hidden-lg&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2><strong>Election Security<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><b>Secure elections are resilient: they can withstand and recover from cyberattacks and other threats.<\/b><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=&#8221;10988&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1687369423741{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;2\/5&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1698075884034{background-color: #ffffff !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}&#8221; offset=&#8221;vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs&#8221;][vc_single_image image=&#8221;10889&#8243; img_size=&#8221;medium&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2><strong>Election Security<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><b>Election security has been a fundamental part of our mission since our founding in 2004. We believe that security, resilience, and verifiability are integral to free and fair elections and that voters should be able to cast an effective ballot without barriers.<\/b><b><\/b><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_separator color=&#8221;custom&#8221; border_width=&#8221;2&#8243; el_width=&#8221;10&#8243; accent_color=&#8221;#969696&#8243;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;3\/5&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1698075891847{background: #ffffff url(https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/Untitled-design-22.png?id=10881) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: contain !important;}&#8221; offset=&#8221;vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs&#8221;][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;400px&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][\/vc_section][vc_row gap=&#8221;25&#8243; equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4 style=\"color: #026da4; text-align: center;\"><strong><span class=\"WdYUQQ text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Election security fundamentally <\/span><\/strong><strong><span class=\"WdYUQQ text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">impacts trust in our elections<\/span><\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_separator color=&#8221;custom&#8221; border_width=&#8221;2&#8243; el_width=&#8221;10&#8243; accent_color=&#8221;#969696&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row gap=&#8221;25&#8243; equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1687456892805{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1687369204887{padding-right: 35px !important;padding-left: 35px !important;background-color: #f2f6fa !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text]<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-10904 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" srcset=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6.png 417w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 60px) 100vw, 60px\" \/>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"WdYUQQ text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Voting technology\u2014like any other technology\u2014might fail, but <strong>strong safeguards<\/strong> and resiliency measures can protect voters and our democracy.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1687369217102{padding-right: 35px !important;padding-left: 35px !important;background-color: #fcfcfc !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text]<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-10904 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" srcset=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6.png 417w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 60px) 100vw, 60px\" \/>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vulnerabilities provide space for attacks on democracy to operate, whether via an actual attack or propagandistic disinformation. The need for <strong>evidence-based elections<\/strong> to counter fears of hacking or claims of fraud has never been clearer.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1687369258021{padding-right: 35px !important;padding-left: 35px !important;background-color: #f2f6fa !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text]<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-10904 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"60\" height=\"60\" srcset=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6.png 417w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography6-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 60px) 100vw, 60px\" \/>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our democracy depends upon <strong>transpartisan work<\/strong> to give the public accurate information about how our elections work. Election officials, government spokespeople, journalists, social media platforms, activists, and civil society organizations must tell the story together.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1688677304716{padding-top: 10px !important;border-radius: 4px !important;}&#8221; el_class=&#8221;red_box&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1695584012237{background-image: url(https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/Untitled-design-10.png?id=11059) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}&#8221; offset=&#8221;vc_hidden-xs&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1698076320758{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-right: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;background-color: #d2e1ed !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4 style=\"color: #026da4;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-10860\" src=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography2.png 200w, https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/VV-Iconography2-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 55px) 100vw, 55px\" \/><strong>About Election Security<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"color: #026da4;\"><span class=\"WdYUQQ text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\"><strong>Secure elections require evidence that voting technology and processes function reliably for voters and that votes were counted as cast. <\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"color: #026da4;\"><span class=\"WdYUQQ text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\">Secure elections are reliable, meaning voters can cast an <strong>effective ballot<\/strong> without barriers. They are <strong>evidence-based<\/strong> and <strong>verifiable<\/strong>, meaning voters have confidence their ballots were received and recorded accurately, and election officials have procedures to check the vote counts. <strong>Transparency<\/strong> throughout the process engenders public trust and ensures fairness. Robust <strong>procedures<\/strong> and <strong>resiliency plans<\/strong> are employed to help ensure voters can continue to vote and are not disenfranchised by long lines or equipment failures.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"color: #026da4;\"><strong>Resilient elections<\/strong> require a way to recover from issues, malfunctions, or problems and still be able to show the correct outcome. The most resilient elections employ <a href=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/paperrecords\/\">paper ballots<\/a> verified by the voter as a true record of voter intent; robust chain of custody for ballots and equipment; strong security measures for both equipment and personnel; and sound <a href=\"https:\/\/verifiedvoting.org\/audits\/\">post-election audits<\/a> to check the election outcome. Read more below in our Election Security 101 series.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1688677322874{padding-top: 20px !important;background-color: #026da4 !important;}&#8221;][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Election Security 101:&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|font_size:35|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; color: white;\"><span class=\"WdYUQQ text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\"><strong>Election security practices that prioritize voters and strengthen our democracy<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; color: white;\"><span class=\"WdYUQQ text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none\"><strong>*Click or swipe for more*<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p>\u00a0[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space]<style type=\"text\/css\" data-type=\"the7_shortcodes-inline-css\">.carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-a8581bfeff23b45f7ac00691b31bb897 .owl-nav a {\n  width: 36px;\n  height: 36px;\n  border-radius: 500px;\n}\n.dt-arrow-border-on.carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-a8581bfeff23b45f7ac00691b31bb897 .owl-nav a:not(:hover):before {\n  border-width: 8px;\n}\n.dt-arrow-hover-border-on.carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-a8581bfeff23b45f7ac00691b31bb897 .owl-nav a:hover:after {\n  border-width: 8px;\n}\n.carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-a8581bfeff23b45f7ac00691b31bb897 .owl-nav a.owl-prev {\n  top: 50%;\n  transform: translateY(calc(-50% + 0px));\n  left: -65px;\n}\n@media all and (-ms-high-contrast: none) {\n  .carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-a8581bfeff23b45f7ac00691b31bb897 .owl-nav a.owl-prev {\n    transform: translateY(-50%);\n    margin-top: 0px;\n  }\n}\n.carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-a8581bfeff23b45f7ac00691b31bb897 .owl-nav a.owl-prev i {\n  padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n}\n.carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-a8581bfeff23b45f7ac00691b31bb897 .owl-nav a.owl-next {\n  top: 50%;\n  transform: translateY(calc(-50% + 0px));\n  right: -65px;\n}\n@media all and (-ms-high-contrast: none) {\n  .carousel-shortcode.carousel-shortcode-id-a8581bfeff23b45f7ac00691b31bb897 .ow